The paper deals with image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of facial expression features to improve the descriptive ability of the model suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the evaluation of the model using standard metrics and analysis of the generated captions suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM).
